ent RF-DC converter paves the way\ntowards the continuous operation of a WSN.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 28 Apr 2017 13:02:31 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 8 Feb 2018 13:47:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-02-09"}
